{"tid":414730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[回家了]牙祖反擊","createTime":"2017-09-26T12:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T12:58:32.000Z","uid":68646,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7310e234736831c7c1e7fcb2b498b5dca253ec4e","tid":414730,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，呢一年唔少會員因手機app體驗不佳而少上高登，我必須承認整件事係我嘅過失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一直有好多熱心會員提供好多優秀嘅建議，只怪我對討論區app經驗不足，未能好好運用會員建議持續改善討論區營運。<br />\n<br />\n為咗彌補問題，呢一年我哋一直都努力改善後台運作，亦留意多咗對高登不離不棄嘅會員寶貴嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。我哋亦聯絡咗之前寫HKGz嘅織菊防Gay巴打合作，希望呢隻app嘅面世可以令高登一眾會員感受到我哋嘅誠意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新版討論區iOS與Android app完成在即，我們決定於下星期舉行封測，封測分兩個部分，包括公開招募及邀請活躍會員參與：<br />\n<br />\n1. PM邀請活躍會員及曾經對官方app給予意見的會員參與封測。<br />\n2. 以此post公開招募，如閣下有興趣參與封測，請PM至「高登公關」（會員ID：586349）提供下列資料，我們將盡量安排所有報名會員參加。<br />\n - iOS用戶：請提供閣下的Apple ID、iPhone型號及iOS版本，我們將提交予Apple作申請封測之用。<br />\n - Android用戶：請提供閣下的手機型號及Android系統版本做紀錄，我們將直接提供程式apk下載網址作手動安裝。<br />\n<br />\n兩個邀請程序現在經已展開，希望各位踴躍參加，謝謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現附上新app iOS版beta的示範短片，部分介面設計並非最終版本：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t-hP6j4SyUs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft-hP6j4SyUs&d=Ct65v9LZ6WpC%2F1HjwhsYJNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6b1c1ee9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t-hP6j4SyUs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6790677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DBW%26message%3D6790677&d=Ct65v9LZ6WpC%2F1HjwhsYJNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a39b356a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6790677</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"29dc23dcbb151ac3285a95163f095e762b4f2060","tid":414730,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"想家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8debaae936d4229fe847ce20a6caf1b2043d4377","tid":414730,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"想念牙祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9702820a816cac9399229b913476d16ffdf655","tid":414730,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:38:59.000Z","msg":"回家了"},{"pid":"6e4bdcaef1b583a5967531923d45ebc17232d158","tid":414730,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"牙祖愛我們，是回家的時候了"},{"pid":"167ba7a4f85de7b226f37145f4fd5a30aa48041f","tid":414730,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:41:06.000Z","msg":"連兵快D課金啦<br />\n<br />\n連登靠你地啦"},{"pid":"1a4f2fce76257650285bf4d4b9055fb0d02c9d9b","tid":414730,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:41:06.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"bb28689c2b67aa9cf136afdcc44a38b0d0d8413c","tid":414730,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"王者歸來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54ccdfb923a27b007b5aec8eecfb723b8beebf8","tid":414730,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:46:52.000Z","msg":"連衛兵繼續留係到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcc2992b071e88e54fecfe6e262aa9b1bafe164","tid":414730,"uid":84834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,